{
  "stem": "13313.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother, who-- by the way, Christian friends who were visiting in this camp where my mother was and they used to smuggle letters in and out also.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when she heard or whatever, knew-- she heard that this-- she knew that I went to that school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That the school was bombed-- she almost went crazy when she thought if I still alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, that's-- so that also helped us to stay alive because we got very close-- as close as we got, to getting caught because we were found out to being Jewish in that school just before the bombardment.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Interesting.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh huh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we are now going to this-- we are now in the fall-- first of all, June of 1944, I hear on the BBC, in the cupboard, between the bomb, bomb, bomb, bombs, scrambling, that there was an invasion in Normandy.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I hear this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The next day, I hear there was an attempt on Hitler.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] All this I, I, I knew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Never talked about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Never said a word.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Roggeman's didn't even know that I knew they had  a radio.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rene was three and 1/2 years younger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was like a baby.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rene was only six-years-old, six and a half.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I did talk with neighbors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Something very ironic happened, which makes this, this little episode so, so paradoxical.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Among our neighbors, we had-- in that population-- especially among the Flemish population-- you had anti-Germans and pro-Germans, collaborators and un-collaborators.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was very difficult to know who was whom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For instance, at the end of the street lived this lady.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She had a little, her little flower garden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And her son was a, was a volunteer for the German SS.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
